{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1db5ba22fc","title":"中山大学右派言论之三：污蔑和攻击肃反运动","origin":"中共中山大学委员会宣传部编: 《中山大学右派言论汇编（一）》，1957年10月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a23f667b7e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"1db5ba22fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f938c570a1","type":"title","text":"中山大学右派言论之三：污蔑和攻击肃反运动","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"ae152b18e2","type":"paragraph","text":"在社会改革运动中，特别是1956年的肃反运动起了副作用，使高级知识分子现在不敢大鸣大放。……肃反运动中所谓的思想批判比1952年的要凶暴得多，不人道得多。……","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"b0e2184d09","type":"paragraph","text":"对于肃反运动的错误性质的估价问题，我不同意官方的说法，以成绩是主要的，错误难免就了事了。我举一个例，就可帮助明白道理，好比有一个医生诊断一百个病人，其中90个医好了，但10个人被错误的弄死了，你能说这个医生的诊疗成绩是主要的吗？","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"237b11a855","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反的责任问题也要弄清楚。……我在北京、武汉、上海三地所了解的情况，肃反运动在高等学校所形成的一切错误，论性质和规模都完全相同，没有二样。实事求是，肃反运动的错误，应由党中央来负责才对。……","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"5df26632c1","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的党就是很忽视法制的，肃反运动暴露出人民政府本身是违反宪法的规定。政府逮捕了教授和一般干部，经过法院审判手续的有几人？共产党人不习惯法制概念。（罗应荣）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"fb3439d180","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反糟多于好，中大被肃反的都是好人，没有一个真正的反革命分子。有些党员藉肃反“大打劫”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"0875623d23","type":"paragraph","text":"中央指出全国99％是好人，百分之几是坏人或反革命的说法不对，肃反的错误中央要负责。（陈乙华）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"16aaac1745","type":"paragraph","text":"这几年来共产党做得最不好的是肃反，特别在宪法公布以后搞肃反，是自己制定宪法，自己又去破坏宪法。（周达仁）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"6354a99631","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反违反宪法。（王宗炎、林式增、刘文、罗木公）","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"f853aaf757","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反就是错误的。（吴重翰）","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"034f923afc","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反时随便抓人，一关就是一年、半年，这是否违反宪法。（张良修）","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"ff200fc0ed","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反时群众斗争，要被斗者低头是违反宪法的。（杨熙旭）","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"74c7e9c440","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反时开群众大会斗人、抓人等都是侵犯人权违反宪法。（梁溢成）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"2e8f4fcbbe","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是有组织、有系统、大规模地破坏宪法。（张志强）","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"f017ab29c3","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是违反宪法，错打许多人，所以在肃反时有许多人自杀、跳河投井，还有信件突然被大搜查的事情。（周奭）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"b6371eaf66","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是违反宪法的，共产党要肃反，最好把宪法推迟2年公布。（麦希尧）","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"7c36499d0f","type":"paragraph","text":"五大运动搞得过火了，肃反虽有成绩，但缺点很大。（蒋耘）","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"5d03b3a713","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是苦打成招。（廖斗南）","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"52115c8ddd","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反打击面太宽，过左一些，党团员及积极分子结合公安局进行大规模搜查翻箱倒箧搞错了很多。（赖增猷）","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"898e956b12","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是扩大化了，肃反是宗派主义，肃反是伤感情的悲剧。（潘亚暾）","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"dcc97b8626","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反定案是完全没有根据。（潘亚暾）","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"241ca30710","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反和思想改造都是打击高级知识分子。（李庾祥）","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"5b9e970485","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反对象被斗是挨“屠夫的屠刀”。（汪廷奎）","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"63a7bcb69e","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反搞得人家街头流浪。（廖斗南）","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"7ba8709a65","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反搞错了，冤枉了好人，肃反不应该在高等学校开展。（陈福荣）","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"dda7e9941d","type":"paragraph","text":"高校肃反应该温和一点。（廖斗南）","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"ea35e72b1a","type":"paragraph","text":"全国的高等学校的肃反都搞错了。（李庾祥）","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"40b2c1248a","type":"paragraph","text":"中国肃反斗争很多人，是因为到处都在找百分之几的反革命分子。（唐友伦）","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"83e57d67d7","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是对青年学生实行精神上的折磨，被斗错的人永不能恢复常态。（罗敬梓）","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"744a3881c2","type":"paragraph","text":"我们那里肃反的时候搞的很多，满街都是死尸，要用卡车一车车的装出去。（潘亚暾）","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"7fb3c7d59e","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反工作偏差是主观主义的结果，客观上是胡适的“大胆假设，小心求证”。（骆传芳）","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"253fb174c8","type":"paragraph","text":"搞运动的劲头很大，做善后工作的劲头却很小。在运动中唯恐炮火不猛烈，运动过后对那些中了流弹，受了误伤的人都没有尽医疗调养的责任。（王宗炎）","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"b9cabb2d72","type":"paragraph","text":"镇反许多人不该枪毙。（罗木公）","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"019dbbfd68","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反时私设公堂（陈庆煌）。隔离反省就是逮捕。（廖光瑀）","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"e5a0cff2ac","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反成绩是次要的，缺点是主要的。（伍锐麟）","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"c2ef8f4685","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是搞糟了，要当时搞肃反的人负责。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"ee783c9aff","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反时党员私设监狱，党员以粪尿给人吃。（杨熙旭）","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"787f83e972","type":"paragraph","text":"在肃反被逮捕后放回来的人，说当初依法逮捕，依他们（指党）要求，要答覆“依法”二字。（詹安泰）","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"d235d50779","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反过左了一些。（顾绶昌）","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"7ce7abaede","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反斗争会是有辱人身，处分是不合法的。（罗木公）","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"f017188cdd","type":"paragraph","text":"从中大肃反错误的比例推算出，全国应有70万人搞错了。（刘绍良）","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"fcc897dcde","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反开展思想批判是错误的，中大肃反100％搞错了。（麦希尧）","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"82b0f5c6a5","type":"paragraph","text":"中大肃反，一片恐怖，使得人人自危。（杨剑侠）","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"655c954a1f","type":"paragraph","text":"中大肃反偏差是主要的，中大肃反不是群众搞的，几个领导对某人有意见就派人搜查材料来搞他。（梁溢成）","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"d918171f68","type":"paragraph","text":"中大肃反有错不认，无反也肃。（周达仁）","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"8bce443395","type":"paragraph","text":"中大的肃反是大胆怀疑，粗心求证，武断贯彻。（端木正）","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"f133f418c0","type":"paragraph","text":"中大的肃反运动缺点是主要的，成绩是次要的。党负责人在总结时还说成绩是主要的，缺点是次要的，这是教条主义。中大搞肃反时，搞了许多人，结果一个人也不是反革命，那能说成绩是主要的呢？（叶启芳）","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"e0274ae124","type":"paragraph","text":"中山大学党领导对肃反运动的估计，都不是实事求是的。（叶启芳）","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"05f2fa564f","type":"paragraph","text":"我们学校肃反90％是搞错了。（邹德勃）","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"6fd5567cb7","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反90％搞错了。（陈伟雄）","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"07a23fce1f","type":"paragraph","text":"全国肃反成绩是主要的，但中大的情况不是这样，是一团糟，这个错了，那个也错了，检讨检讨就算了。（张绪穗）","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"42df7ce93f","type":"paragraph","text":"刘雪明是龙潜迫死的。（谭寄南）","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"561bdce701","type":"paragraph","text":"刘雪明之死应该完全由当时党委书记龙潜负责，她是一个年青的女孩子，龙潜这样对待她，当然会自杀。（潘保璠）","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"e647287115","type":"paragraph","text":"为死者伸冤，为生者求保障。（李宗武）","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"32d000c174","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风不是反革命集团，要为胡风集团伸冤。（刘法生）","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"9183cc0739","type":"paragraph","text":"对胡风集团是不是反革命集团有怀疑。（梁礼谦）","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"25dde6b7ae","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风是不是反革命？还要等待历史证明。（姚龙波）","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"c0fac8d7d1","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风不是反革命，只是文艺思想问题。（江建文）","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"9c969749af","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风不是反革命，只是共产党作家对他的打击。（汪祖受）","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"5df4de7c20","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风反革命案件是假的。（杨宗焜）","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"3c314def75","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风事件只是宗派主义的活动，是文艺界的不和睦，只不过是胡风对手得势而已。（陈庆煌）","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"d7cd3117ba","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风问题是宗派主义活动，不是反革命集团，和朱光潜问题是一样。（罗滏光）","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"9b24dc5e14","type":"paragraph","text":"只根据所发表出来的3批材料，不足以证明胡风为反革命分子。（陈世伊）","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"},{"id":"5356f4fb90","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风是反革命，但说胡风集团是反革命集团就不能令人信服。（罗滏光）","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc"}],"page":{"id":"8dbd6021c7","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1db5ba22fc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}